-- Oettinger Seeks EU Rig Safety Rules, Frankfurter Allgemeine Says
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-03-29T17:18:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-29/oettinger-seeks-eu-rig-safety-rules-frankfurter-allgemeine-says.html
The European Union should agree on
stricter safety rules for pumping oil and natural gas to be
applied across the bloc,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung  cited
European Energy Commissioner  Guenther Oettinger  as saying.  The regulation of offshore drilling rigs is largely on a
national basis, the Frankfurt-based newspaper said in an e-
mailed summary of an article to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nicholas Comfort in Frankfurt at 
 ncomfort1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  